《'''壹號皇庭III'''》（[[英語|英文]]：{{lang|en|The File of Justice III}}），[[香港|香港]][[無綫電視|無綫電視]][[翡翠台|翡翠台]]時裝法律[[電視劇|電視劇]]，於1994年10月9日首播，共20集，監製[[鄧特希|鄧特希]]。初時逢星期日晚播出，後調至星期三晚22：00後綜藝時段播出。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mooddiary.pixnet.net/blog/post/32693582-%E5%A3%B9%E8%99%9F%E7%9A%87%E5%BA%AD%E3%80%81%E5%A3%B9%E8%99%9F%E7%9A%87%E5%BA%ADii%E3%80%81%E5%A3%B9%E8%99%9F%E7%9A%87%E5%BA%ADiii%E3%80%81%E5%A3%B9%E8%99%9F%E7%9A%87 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2018-01-08 |archive-date=2018-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180207122446/http://mooddiary.pixnet.net/blog/post/32693582-%e5%a3%b9%e8%99%9f%e7%9a%87%e5%ba%ad%e3%80%81%e5%a3%b9%e8%99%9f%e7%9a%87%e5%ba%adii%e3%80%81%e5%a3%b9%e8%99%9f%e7%9a%87%e5%ba%adiii%e3%80%81%e5%a3%b9%e8%99%9f%e7%9a%87 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://tvcity.tvb.com/drama/just3/index.htm   File of Justice III   壹 號 皇 庭 III] {{Wayback|url=http://tvcity.tvb.com/drama/just3/index.htm |date=20080917055940 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20161006/55736986 |title=【《壹號皇庭》女星搖籃】 宣萱陳慧珊榮升花旦 Sammi王菲雄霸樂壇 |access-date=2018-01-08 |archive-date=2018-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108174837/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20161006/55736986 |dead-url=no }}</ref><REF>[https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82/95575/-%E4%B8%80%E9%A6%96%E6%AD%8C-%E6%9E%97%E4%BF%9D%E6%80%A1-%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9-%E8%AC%9B%E5%88%86%E6%89%8B%E5%82%B7%E7%97%9B-%E6%88%91%E4%BB%8D%E7%84%B6%E7%95%99%E4%BD%8F%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6   【一首歌】林保怡《和你的每一天》講分手傷痛：我仍然留住記憶]</REF>

